author: asmuts
msg: Solved most of the group problems created from cleanup by adding an

updateExclude method to the cache hub to allow for exclusion from non local caches.  The group cache is more concerned about where an item came from.  It needs to be able to control the hub without lying to it.  I didn't want to have the group cache lie and say that an item was nonlocal just so it wouldn't get propagated.
More honest now.  Much easier to understand and keep track of.  Will clean further tomorrow.
Need to see if the sessions are replicaitng properly tomorrow.
